liveBlogPostPrepared.plaintext: You might recognise the comedian from AFL talk show The Front Bar and his appearances on Have You Been Paying Attention? Now Sam Pang is taking on the Logies as the first solo host in 11 years. The 2023 ceremony also marks the first time in more than 30 years that the Logies will be hosted in Sydney. When the location was announced, outgoing New South Wales premier D﻿ominic Perrottet said it would be a game-changer for the state. "This will inject millions of dollars into the NSW economy, creating hundreds of jobs in production, hospitality and events,” he said.
